The '''''Liberator''-class troopship''' was a troop transport.

==History==
The class was used by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] during its final years.
At least [[Liberator (Liberator-class)|one vessel]] was refurbished as a smuggler ship following the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

